2017-11-26T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係先達做過學師，見老細日搵4千幾</blockquote><br />\n咁你嗰時月薪幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白紙入去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n使唔使讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10k ，咩都唔識入去<br />\n<br />\n最後升返大學，冇再做"},{"pid":"fdd8a5f7bdb992c4d789539c951b430aaafef2be","tid":480753,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係先達做過學師，見老細日搵4千幾</blockquote><br />\n咁你嗰時月薪幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白紙入去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n使唔使讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n10k ，咩都唔識入去<br />\n<br />\n最後升返大學，冇再做</blockquote><br />\n知唔知頂薪幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一日返幾多個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bae41e3df747cf91b4164059018e4cdf14c44a","tid":480753,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef857fe1fa84f68b61c930205c903b8d8df0e4c","tid":480753,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登係咪冇人做呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2659b6cc74dff0391cc0159965ad53c920d7a4f","tid":480753,"uid":74185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:14:43.000Z","msg":"做過，睇你做街果d定牌子代理維修果d，<br />\n牌子代理維修好hea，根本只係知咩問題就換果樣零件，但要升呢，就要識電子野。<br />\n<br />\n街果d就多一點點技術，不過就只有自己開到先有前途<br />\n<br />\n兩種人工都低"},{"pid":"45ab5904299d9d400aa61d058a33c8c297f73a33","tid":480753,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"學徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n技術水平仲低過富士康班員工<br />\n上Youtube跟住拆，換件，裝返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n零件咪又係淘寶貨<br />\n賺錢最主要都係食零件價差"},{"pid":"74169b827674faf5ef8c049d89c78ea6b99784a6","tid":480753,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"轉自香討<br />\n<br />\n老實講,..依家o係香港, 手機已經冇人會 &quot;維修&quot;<br />\n最多都只係換下 parts, <br />\n唔同當年, 電話大大舊, 價錢貴, 但電路簡單, <br />\n維修只要一支 &quot;辣雞&quot;, 通常都係換下電容, 它下塊板有冇甩甩漏漏, 度到邊度有問題就整邊度<br />\n如果唔係電容電阻, 咪又係成塊板換!!<br />\n<br />\n但依家電話, 線路複雜, 仲有program, 絕不容易理解 (破解)<br />\no係人工貴, parts 平 o既情況下, 邊仲會同你慢慢check 機?<br />\n壞機 一係成部換, 一係上大陸或上淘寶搵零件....<br />\n<br />\nmon壞換mon, logic board 壞就換 logic board....如果換晒都係唔得就成部換<br />\n想要拆機manual 上網 google 一下, 咩model 都搵得到<br />\n<br />\n電子科技已完全傾向電腦化<br />\n唔會再有 &quot;簡單電路&quot; 亦唔會再有 &quot;維修師傅&quot;<br />\n入行做 &quot;手機維修&quot; 千萬不要當係 &quot;一技傍身&quot;, <br />\n正如你入行做洗碗同掃街, 真係搵個阿豬阿狗都頂到你<br />\n長遠計定必是死路一條"},{"pid":"1a6762a61896eefd5426104a073c5161ece108a7","tid":480753,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n技術水平仲低過富士康班員工<br />\n上Youtube跟住拆，換件，裝返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n零件咪又係淘寶貨<br />\n賺錢最主要都係食零件價差</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}